    <div class="howitworks-header">
      <span class="label-pill">How it works for CPAs</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">From signup to a full tax season, <span class="accent">in 3 steps.</span></h2>
      <p class="lede">No long onboarding. No SEO meetings. Connect once, watch your local presence run itself.</p>
