    <div class="step-block">
      <div class="step-grid">
        <div class="step-text">
          <div class="step-meta"><span class="step-num">01</span><span class="step-day">Day 1 · 5 minutes</span></div>
          <h3 class="h-md">Tell theStacc <span class="accent">about your practice.</span></h3>
          <p>Service mix (1040s, S-Corps, bookkeeping), your city, your service area, your typical client. theStacc generates your tax-season keyword map and 90-day content calendar.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>CPA-tuned setup (not generic local SEO)</li>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>1-click GBP + WordPress connect</li>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>Tax-season calendar mapped out to April 15</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="step-visual">
          <div class="step-card-1">
            <div class="step-card-header"><span class="step-card-tag">PRACTICE PROFILE · 4 MIN</span><span class="step-card-status">● Complete</span></div>
            <div class="step-card-row"><span class="step-card-key">Firm</span><span class="step-card-val">Hayes &amp; Co CPAs · 6 staff</span></div>
            <div class="step-card-row"><span class="step-card-key">Services</span><span class="step-card-val">1040 · S-Corp · QBO bookkeeping</span></div>
            <div class="step-card-row"><span class="step-card-key">Service area</span><span class="step-card-val">Boise, ID · 25-mile radius</span></div>
            <div class="step-card-row"><span class="step-card-key">Brand voice</span><span class="step-card-val">Trusted · Plain-English · Local</span></div>
            <div class="step-card-row highlight"><span class="step-card-key">Output</span><span class="step-card-val"><strong>68-keyword map · April-15 calendar</strong></span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-block">
      <div class="step-grid reverse">
        <div class="step-text">
          <div class="step-meta"><span class="step-num">02</span><span class="step-day">Every week · Auto-pilot</span></div>
          <h3 class="h-md">Articles + GBP posts <span class="accent">ship while you file returns.</span></h3>
          <p>You handle the 1040s. theStacc handles the marketing. Every week, new tax articles publish, GBP posts go live, and review responses ship — without you touching the dashboard.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>30 tax-season articles per month</li>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>Daily GBP posts about deadlines, deductions</li>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>Reviews replied to within 30 minutes</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="step-visual">
          <div class="step-card-2">
            <div class="step-card-header"><span class="step-card-tag">THIS WEEK · LIVE FEED</span><span class="step-card-status">● Auto</span></div>
            <div class="step-feed-item"><span class="step-feed-dot done"></span><span class="step-feed-time">Mon 09:14</span><span class="step-feed-text">Article live · <strong>"2026 tax bracket changes"</strong></span></div>
            <div class="step-feed-item"><span class="step-feed-dot done"></span><span class="step-feed-time">Mon 12:30</span><span class="step-feed-text">GBP post · Q4 estimates deadline reminder</span></div>
            <div class="step-feed-item"><span class="step-feed-dot done"></span><span class="step-feed-time">Tue 08:02</span><span class="step-feed-text">5★ review replied · 2 min response</span></div>
            <div class="step-feed-item"><span class="step-feed-dot done"></span><span class="step-feed-time">Wed 09:00</span><span class="step-feed-text">Article live · <strong>"S-Corp election deadlines"</strong></span></div>
            <div class="step-feed-item"><span class="step-feed-dot live"></span><span class="step-feed-time">Now</span><span class="step-feed-text">LinkedIn post · scheduled 3 PM today</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="step-block">
      <div class="step-grid">
        <div class="step-text">
          <div class="step-meta"><span class="step-num">03</span><span class="step-day">By October · Year-end surge</span></div>
          <h3 class="h-md">Year-end clients <span class="accent">find your firm first.</span></h3>
          <p>By October, you're ranking for "CPA near me," "tax preparation [your city]," and 36 more local terms. New small-biz owners searching for a year-end accountant book with you. Your tax season is half-booked before January.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>Map Pack top 3 — 92% of firms hit it in 90 days</li>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>+38 ranked local keywords on average</li>
            <li><span class="icon"><svg><use href="#i-check"/></svg></span>Friday report — what worked, what booked</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="step-visual">
          <div class="step-card-3">
            <div class="step-card-header"><span class="step-card-tag">90-DAY OUTCOME</span><span class="step-card-status">● Live</span></div>
            <div class="step-stat-big">
              <span class="step-stat-num">47</span>
              <span class="step-stat-label">New client inquiries / mo</span>
              <span class="step-stat-delta">↑ 312% vs Day 1</span>
            </div>
            <div class="step-stat-row">
              <div><strong>38</strong> KW ranked</div>
              <div><strong>#2</strong> Map Pack</div>
              <div><strong>$14k</strong> new MRR</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BENEFITS — what an accountant gets -->
  <section class="benefits-section">
    <div class="benefits-header">
      <span class="label-pill">03 · What you get</span>
      <h2 class="h-lg">Built for the <span class="accent">CPA's calendar.</span></h2>
      <p class="lede">Outcomes that matter to accounting firms: tax-season leads, year-end clients, Map Pack visibility, and a blog that ranks while you file.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="benefits-grid">
      <div class="benefit-cell">
        <div class="benefit-icon-box"><svg><use href="#i-trend"/></svg></div>
