      </div>
      <div class="benefit-cell">
        <div class="benefit-icon-box"><svg><use href="#i-dollar"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="h-sm">Lower cost than an agency.</h3>
        <p>Replace your $3,000/mo local-SEO agency. Same outcome at 3% of the price.</p>
        <div class="benefit-stat"><div class="benefit-stat-num">$40<span class="accent">k+</span></div><div class="benefit-stat-label">SAVED VS AGENCY / YR</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-cell">
        <div class="benefit-icon-box"><svg><use href="#i-clock"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="h-sm">Hands-free during tax season.</h3>
        <p>Articles, posts, and review replies ship while you do returns. Zero marketing meetings.</p>
        <div class="benefit-stat"><div class="benefit-stat-num">0<span class="accent">h</span></div><div class="benefit-stat-label">OF YOUR TIME / WEEK</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="benefit-cell">
        <div class="benefit-icon-box"><svg><use href="#i-target"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="h-sm">Year-end pipeline.</h3>
